FT  05 NOV 94 / UK Company News: En-tout-cas expands
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
En-tout-cas has agreed a deal with Balsam of Germany which will, the company
says, create a major player in the world market for synthetic sports
surfaces and allied sports equipment.
The new company, ETC (Holdings), will have an initial annual turnover
exceeding Pounds 50m and gross assets of more than Pounds 22m.
