<HEADLINE>
FT  04 NOV 94 / UK Company News: Grafton acquisition
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Grafton Group, the Dublin-based builders' merchant, has acquired Lumley &amp;
Hunt, a Sussex-based plumbing and heating merchant, for Pounds 1.6m in cash
and loan notes.
Lumley has an annual turnover of Pounds 6.5m and has recently been making
losses. The consideration is below asset value.
