FT  04 NOV 94 / UK Company News: Enterprise Computer
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Enterprise Computer Holdings, which incurred losses of Pounds 2m last year
and saw revenues fall from Pounds 58m to Pounds 16.4m after extensive
